videos.headline: Texas A&M WR Tabuyo makes tremendous one-handed catch
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Trevor Knight throws a 29-yard pass to WR Jeremy Tabuyo who comes down with an incredible one-handed catch to get the first down on the play.

videos.headline: South Carolina head coach Will Muschamp is happy with his defense's effort
videos.description: South Carolina head coach Will Muschamp is happy with his defense's effort

videos.headline: Williams' big-time scamper puts Texas A&M ahead
videos.description: Trayveon Williams slices through the South Carolina defense and finishes off the run with a hurdle over the last defender to find the end zone, putting Texas A&M ahead 14-7.

videos.headline: Texas A&M tops South Carolina to stay undefeated
videos.description: Trayveon Williams rushes for 98 yards and a touchdown as No. 9 Texas A&M improves to 5-0 with a 24-13 victory over South Carolina.
